    Class representing the book add window, used for adding new books to the database.

    ClientList
    Class representing the client tab in the admin menu, consists of a table with all the clients, sort and filter methods as well as add and edit functions.
    DatabaseHelper
    Helper class for handling operations with the MySQL Database.
    Inventory
